.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.IX Header "SYNOPSIS"
.Vb 1
\&  use C4::Auth_with_ldap;
.Ve
.SH "LDAP Configuration"
.IX Header "LDAP Configuration"
.Vb 5
\&    This module is specific to LDAP authentification. It requires Net::LDAP package and one or more
\&        working LDAP servers.
\&        To use it :
